co.cask.cdap.api.procedure

Class AbstractProcedure

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.api.procedure.AbstractProcedure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Procedure, ProgramLifecycle<ProcedureContext>
    Deprecated. 
    As of version 2.6.0, replaced by AbstractService

    @Deprecated
public abstract class AbstractProcedure
extends Object
implements Procedure
    An abstract implementation of the Procedure interface. This class is preferrable to Procedure interface if you don't have have complex logic during initialization and destoying of Procedure.

    This class implements initialize(ProcedureContext), destroy() and configure()

    See Also:
    Procedure
